---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure"
  description="How MyTripTip earns revenue through affiliate partnerships and what that means for you."
>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12 prose prose-slate">
    <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>

    <p>
      MyTripTip is a free resource. To keep it that way, some links on this site are
      affiliate links. When you click these links and make a purchase or booking, we may
      receive a small commission at no additional cost to you.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Partners</h2>
    <p>We currently partner with the following platforms:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Booking.com</strong> — hotel and accommodation bookings</li>
      <li><strong>Viator</strong> — tours, activities, and experiences</li>
      <li><strong>Airalo</strong> — eSIM plans for international travelers</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      We may add additional partners in the future. This page will be updated accordingly.
    </p>

    <h2>What This Means for You</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>You pay the same price whether you use our links or not.</li>
      <li>We only recommend products and services we believe are genuinely useful.</li>
      <li>Affiliate relationships do not influence our editorial recommendations.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Advertising</h2>
    <p>
      Some pages on this site display advertisements through Google AdSense. These ads
      are clearly distinguishable from editorial content.
    </p>

    <p>
      Questions about our partnerships? <a href="/contact/">Get in touch</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
